sequenceDiagram
    participant SF as Salesforce
    participant AUTH as Auth Platform
    participant API as Downstream API

    SF->>AUTH: Submit signed JWT with `source_role`
    Note right of AUTH: Extract `source_role` from request token
    AUTH-->>SF: Return new access token with `role` claim
    SF->>API: Call API with issued token (includes `role`)
    API-->>API: Enforce RBAC based on `role` claim
